You can use the Weekly Plan feature of Scrum-tous! coordinate meals with your friends and family.
1. From the main menu, select "Weekly Plan".
2. Select the date of the meal you want to share.
3. Select the meal you wish to share.
4. Select the "Share" button on the top right of the screen.
5. Enter the email addresses of the people you want to share this meal with, then press "Send". An email will be sent to the entered email addresses with an invitation to the shared meal.
